{"tid":1552942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉江華：林鄭冀本月內落區面對面對話","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:55:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"ffedeee6e656a5ef1de8af7734070c1d859a698a","tid":1552942,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:38:44.000Z","msg":"民政事務局局長劉江華表示，政府正設計一個可與市民對話的平台，特首林鄭月娥希望在本月內，能落區與市民進行面對面的互動交流。<br />\n<br />\n劉江華出席活動後稱，期望對話有建設性，能給予啟示社會應如何走下去，如就對話方式有結果，會盡快公布。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，作出有關安排時有多個難題要處理，例如要在短時間內走遍18區需要較長時間，因此正研究如何將部分區組合起來。另外，由於希望持不同意見人士都能在特首面前表達意見，因此要考慮如何作出公開邀請。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，本港社會的整體環境，已較早前略靜了一些，大多數市民都希望有一個寧靜的環境及社會回復正常秩序。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2245268/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2245268%2F&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMKxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=4d06e7af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2245268/</a>"},{"pid":"e8f5bedda1280d128b1f5b794d1412f1da81df86","tid":1552942,"uid":245033,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRUBm2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRUBm2S.jpg&h=1a20143f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58ff070f5f3b380c71723666743d498bae160d1d","tid":1552942,"uid":158960,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌"},{"pid":"ecf4db4d4d90c5f5f3de1a12a4e4834a1070c879","tid":1552942,"uid":78769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e8f5bedda1280d128b1f5b794d1412f1da81df86","tid":1552942,"uid":245033,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRUBm2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRUBm2S.jpg&h=1a20143f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:40:21.00